  <brief_title>Far Infrared Radiation Treatment for Uterine Fibroids</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1 Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of Using Energy Specific Far Infrared Radiation Treatment for Uterine Fibroids</official_title>
