  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women age 18 or older with symptomatic fibroids

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Women who are pregnant, as confirmed by serum test at time of screening, or urine
             pregnancy test on the day of treatment

          -  Metallic implants that are incompatible with MRI or ultrasound

          -  Known intolerance to the MRI contrast agent (e.g. Gadolinium)
      </textblock>
